        <h2 class="card-title h4">About FUPRE</h2>
        <p>The Federal University of Petroleum Resources, Effurun (FUPRE), established in 2007, is the first of its kind in Africa and sixth in the world. It is a specialized federal university located in Delta State, Nigeria, with a focus on petroleum engineering and technology.</p>
        
        <h2 class="card-title h4 mt-4">Portal Usage Instructions</h2>
        <p>This portal is designed to provide easy access to official information. Use the navigation bar to access different sections:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Home:</strong> Get a quick overview of the latest memos and upcoming events.</li>
          <li><strong>Memos:</strong> View all official announcements and circulars from the university management.</li>
          <li><strong>Calendar:</strong> Keep track of the academic calendar, including important dates and events.</li>
          <li><strong>Search:</strong> Use the search bar in the header to quickly find specific information.</li>
        </ul>
